Package edu.columbia.stat.wood.pub.util

Interface Summary
IntDiscreteDistribution Int discrete distribution interface.
 

Class Summary
DoubleStack Stack object for double native types.
IntHashMapDiscreteDistribution Implementation of a discrete distribution over an integer valued state space.
IntMap<E> Array based map for native int keys.
IntUniformDiscreteDistribution Uniform discrete distribution over the integers in [leftType, rightType).
LogAdd Method to provide the static function logAdd which is useful when arithmetic has to be done on the log scale.
LogBracketFunction Class to provide static method to get the log of the bracket function often used when discussing the score of a seating arrangement for the Chinese restaurant process.
LogGeneralizedSterlingNumbers Class to provide method to get the log of a generalized sterling number.
MersenneTwisterFast MersenneTwister and MersenneTwisterFast
MutableDouble Container class for double which can be set and manipulated.
MutableInt Container class for int which allows the underlying value to be set.
Pair<F,S> Container class for two objects.
SampleWithoutReplacement Class to provide static method to return a random ordering of the integers 1 - n.
SeatingArranger Class to provide static method to get a seating arrangement sampled according to the Chinese restaurant process, conditioned on the number of customers, number of tables and discount parameter.
